Rampage receives the transmission from Brightblade.
Rampage: An excellent idea sub-commander. I will take command of our small 
groups, and I will have Scourge and Mosquitor analyze the data as soon as we 
get it. I believe there has been a change of plans Megatron we won't be 
following you. Auto-guns fire!
The Autoguns all point at Megatron and fire there all.
Rampage: Tankorr escort Megatron out of here.
Tankorr: TANKORR ESCORT!!!!! IN PIECES!!!!
Tankorr drives out of the base and also fires at Megatron.
